Constructor Detail

DebugSubscriberListener

public DebugSubscriberListener()
Create a DebugSubscriberListener that prints all callback calls. Callbacks that you want printed should be ORed into this printMask from values found in StatusKind.

DebugSubscriberListener

public DebugSubscriberListener(int printMask)
Create a DebugSubscriberListener with the specified printMask. Callbacks that you want printed should be ORed into this printMask from values found in StatusKind.
